Develop an AI-powered autoblog content creation tool that automates the process of generating, curating, and publishing blog posts. Key features include: 1. Automated scraping of latest AI and tech news from specified sources, 2. Advanced AI algorithms for content summarization and generation, 3. User-friendly UI for content review and selection, 4. Integration of SEO optimization techniques for content, 5. Capability to generate accompanying AI-created images, and 6. A complete package for final review and easy blog post publication.